Templates use the SimpleTemplate (or stpl) engine from bottle.py.
http://bottlepy.org/docs/dev/stpl.html
The actual templates (*.tpl files) are generated by pretrans.py from pre-templates (*.ptp files).
Pre-templates include the [[*]] construct for localized strings.
pretrans.py changes every [[*]] in *.ptp files to {{_(*)}}, creating the corresponding *.tpl files.
